name: Treacle 001
description:
This is the launch top from treacle clothing.

Treacle clothing is a British, Midlands based clothing label launched in 2010. This custom hand finished t shirt is printed on 100% organic Indian cotton shirt and hand printed in Birmingham and then finished in our small factory in the Midlands. We print and finish fifty T shirts so there super limited edition. We print on water based ink, our inks do not contain any toxic chemicals at all. 
The shirt is sent to you inside our collectors box with a certificate of authenticity and numbered, then packed with care with a couple of stickers.
Consider the effects of domestic machine washing and tumble drying.  
SAVE THE CLIMATE – WASH COOL – LINE DRY
